        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Set the callback for dwDTERate SetLineCoding requests. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><xrefsect id="deprecated_1_deprecated000010"><xreftitle>Deprecated</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>Use <ref refid="group__usbd__api" kindref="compound">USB device core API</ref> and <ref refid="group__usbd__msg__api_1ggaa9163408c0006825575a919322f25f56a820f9547e0db4baea563dca9c211f9b1" kindref="member">USBD_MSG_CDC_ACM_LINE_CODING</ref> instead.</para>
</xrefdescription></xrefsect></para>
<para>The callback is invoked when the USB host changes the baud rate.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This function is available only when CONFIG_CDC_ACM_DTE_RATE_CALLBACK_SUPPORT is enabled.</para>
</simplesect>
